<HL>
   Pier 1 Sales Increase
</HL>
<DATE>
09/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C9
</SO>
<CO>
   PIR
</CO>
<IN>
SPECIALTY RETAILERS (OTS)
</IN>
<LP>
   FORT WORTH, Texas -- Pier 1 Imports Inc. said sales for
the second quarter ended Sept.2 increased 11%, to $149.6
million from $134.9 million. Sales at stores open more than a
year increased 4.1%. Pier One is a specialty retailer of home
furnishings.
   ---
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Corrections &amp; Amplifications
                                                                                                       

   PIER 1 IMPORTS Inc.'s sales for the second quarter ended
Sept. 2 at stores open at least one year declined 4.1%. The
figure was given as an increase in yesterday's edition.
   (WSJ Sept. 14, 1990)
